<pre id="mwMQ">   0101
OR 0011
 = 0111</pre>

<p id="mwMg"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/C_(프로그래밍_언어)" title="C (프로그래밍 언어)" id="mwMw">C</a> / <a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/C++" title="C++" id="mwNA">C++</a></p>
<pre id="mwNQ">x = y | z;</pre>

<p id="mwNg"><a rel="mw:WikiLink" href="//ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/델파이" title="델파이" id="mwNw">델파이</a></p>
<pre id="mwOA">x := y or z;</pre>

</section><section data-mw-section-id="3" id="mwOQ" aria-labelledby="XOR"><div class="mw-heading mw-heading2"><h2 id="XOR">XOR</h2><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="//ko.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=%EB%B9%84%ED%8A%B8_%EC%97%B0%EC%82%B0&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3" title="부분 편집: XOR"><span>편집</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>

<p id="mwOg"><b id="mwOw">XOR</b> 연산은 두 값의 각 자릿수를 비교해, 값이 같으면 0, 다르면 1을 계산한다.</p>

<table class="wikitable" id="mwPA">
<tbody id="mwPQ"><tr id="mwPg"><th id="mwPw">비트 1</th>
<th id="mwQA">비트 2</th>
<th id="mwQQ">결과</th></tr>
<tr id="mwQg">
<td id="mwQw">0</td>
